m-nfl-for-not-booking-lil-wayne-for-2025-super-bowl-halftime-show-3792185">Birdman, Drake, Nicki Minaj and more called for the NFL to reverse the decision and choose Wayne</a> to headline this weekend&#39;s Super Bowl halftime show. Lamar commented on the backlash on &#39;Wacced Out Murals&#39; from <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/kendrick-lamar-gnx-review-3815647">his latest album, &#39;Gnx&#39;</a> – <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lil-wayne-responds-to-being-namechecked-on-kendrick-lamars-wacced-out-murals-wtf-i-do-3815299">which confused Wayne, who tweeted, “Wtf I do?” in response to the song</a> .</p><p> Since then, Wayne has <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lil-wayne-says-he-and-kendrick-lamar-have-spoken-about-the-2025-super-bowl-he-better-kill-it-3822805">revealed he and Lamar have settled the score over the whole Super Bowl saga</a> , telling Skip Bayless: “I wish him all the best and I told him he better kill it. He gotta kill it.”</p><p> Kendrick&#39;s 2025 NFL Super Bowl LIX halftime show will take place this Sunday (February 9) <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kendrick-lamar-confirms-sza-as-special-guest-for-super-bowl-performance-3831623">with special guest SZA</a> . <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kendrick-lamar-on-what-to-expect-from-his-storytelling-super-bowl-halftime-show-3836015">拉马尔（Lamar）在接受Apple Music的新采访中说，球迷可以期望他带来“洛杉矶能量”</a> ，并热衷于将他的讲故事技巧带到最前沿。</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lil-wayne-reveals-the-carter-vi-will-be-out-this-summer-june-3836029">Lil Wayne announces release date for &#39;The Carter VI&#39;</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
