r drew a single breath upon this Earth 。”</p><p> While it remains to be seen exactly what this means for Irving, this probably means Irving&#39;s Innie will cease to exist. His outie, however, will be alive and well.</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/severance-season-2-episode-4-explained-helly-outie-3835789">&#39;Severance&#39; season two episode four explained: was Helly actually her outie?</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
